; Test Lane 2 — NGKs Crater Wardens V1
; Phase 9: Level Build
; ----------------------------------------------------------------
; Layout (ground surface at Y=550):
;
;   x=-400 ── x=1900  GAP1(400px)  x=2300 ─── x=3800  GAP2(400px)  x=4200 ── x=6200
;    GroundL2Left        ↑long       GroundL2Mid   ↑long              GroundL2Right
;
;   Mine:   x=600, 1450, 2600, 3000
;   Hover:  x=900, 1650, 3500
;   Drone:  (2350,380), (3600,380)
;   Turret: x=2800, 4300
;   PlatA:  x=1200, y=490  (jump-chain start)
;   PlatB:  x=1420, y=490  (jump-chain end, ~220 px CC)
;   PlatC:  x=3300, y=490  (section 5 platform)
;   HazardGap1: (2100, 620) below Gap1
;   HazardGap2: (4000, 620) below Gap2
;   CP1: x=1500 | CP2: x=3000 | CP3: x=4300
;   Finish: x=4700
; ----------------------------------------------------------------

